#: modules/ROOT/pages/technical-infrastructure.adoc:47
msgid ""
"This means from the outset the City Council having the URL that will serve "
"to identify the project under its control.  Even if the project website is "
"hosted by a site such as GitHub, redirecting it will enable the same address "
"to be kept public if it is decided to move the development website in the "
"future."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/technical-infrastructure.adoc:49
msgid "There are two options:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/technical-infrastructure.adoc:51
